        <p>These terms and conditions are governed by and construed in accordance with applicable laws and you irrevocably submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in that location. If any provision of these terms shall be unlawful, void, or unenforceable, then that provision shall be deemed severable and shall not affect the validity of the remaining provisions.</p>
